                        <scopecontent>
                            <p>Reports; Official documentation</p>
                            <p>Orders of the Day (Tagesbefehle) issued by the Aeltestenrat (Council
                                of Elders) in Theresienstadt, 12/1941-06/1942, and other material
                                The file includes: Orders of the Day, Nos. 1-150, dealing with,
                                among other matters, the structure of the independent
                                administration; living arrangements in the ghetto; housing and work
                                arrangements; notices regarding transports; verdicts issued by the
                                court of law of the independent administration; notices regarding
                                deaths. The file also includes: - Announcements by the ghetto
                                administration regarding the organization of the ghetto headed by
                                Jacob Edelstein and Otto Zucker, 05 December 1941; - Memorandum
                                regarding the powers of the Aeltestenrat; 02 June 1943; - List of
                                members of the Aeltestenrat, September 1944; - Report regarding
                                possible methods for conveying information.</p>
